stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle

  Idle --> DataIngestion : Start Data Stream
  DataIngestion --> Monitoring : Data Received
  Monitoring --> FaultDetected : Anomaly Found
  Monitoring --> NormalOperation : No Anomaly

  FaultDetected --> MaintenanceAnalysis : Analyze Fault
  MaintenanceAnalysis --> PredictiveMaintenance : Condition-Based Rule
  MaintenanceAnalysis --> PreventiveMaintenance : Time-Based Rule
  MaintenanceAnalysis --> ReactiveMaintenance : Immediate Issue

  PredictiveMaintenance --> TaskScheduling : Generate Work Order
  PreventiveMaintenance --> TaskScheduling
  ReactiveMaintenance --> TaskScheduling

  TaskScheduling --> Notification : Notify PMS / Technician
  Notification --> Logging : Record in MongoDB/PostgreSQL
  Logging --> Reporting : Update Dashboard / Reports
  Reporting --> Idle : Return to Monitoring State

  NormalOperation --> Logging : Store Regular Data
  Logging --> Idle : Wait for Next Event
